<a href="/articles/25826.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/25826/indexMediumPc2/25826.jpg?1461221416" alt="想喝薯片味的可乐吗？日本这家游戏公司做出来了">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/5/medium/5.png?1411569637" alt="城市">
			<span>城市</span>
		</p>
